ch components off her, so put out an invite to head over there and check it out, take the components off his hands.  Ah, what the heck, I was bound next to the Lake Rathe zone in SK, so gated over there, through Lake Rathetear, Rathe Mountains, finding my way to Feerott, home of the ogres, which I had been to several times.  I head straight south and Oake says he'll come and get me.  I get there and he's taking out the 2 spectres from the tunnel there.  I watched in awe as he skillfully dispatched the 2 creatures of death.  We make our way through a little maze, and wind up in the area that holds the portal to the Plane of Fear.  Oake quickly kills the necro and her pet, and we go sit down right next to the portal, with me being invis the whole time.  I kept Oake breezed, even though he didn't lose much mana during his fights with her, and received some words and pages for research.  It was fun watching Oake kill the necro, ideally before she summoned a pet.  After a while I was starting to get sleepy, so before I left I jumped into the portal to Fear!  Fortunately I wasn't able to enter the plane due to the fact I'm only 27th level, so it put me to a spot just south of Oggok, the ogre city.  Someone needed a bind in Oggok, so I did that for him, then camped out.  My thanks to Oake for showing me the area, was quite the little adventure! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bthecounciloftwilight.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cashewribs>CashewRibs</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/4/01 11:53:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: So close to the planes</span><hr size=1> Interesting.  I didn't know you have to be a certain level to reach the planes.  Which sorta does make sense.  Probably prevents massive newbie deaths and super uber twinking (not that there's anything wrong with that).  What level do you need to be to reach the planes?<br>
<br>
Curious Cashew <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bthecounciloftwilight.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=loralana>Loralana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/4/01 12:50:39 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: So close to the planes</span><hr size=1> You must be 46th level to enter any of the planes (Fear, Hate and Sky).  I don't know for sure about Mischief and Growth, but I imagine they would be the same, and the surrounding areas are definitely geared to those levels.<br>
<br>
Loralana Mystere<br>
28th season enchantress <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm3.showMessage?topicID=6.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm3.threadControl?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub25.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm2">Character Bios<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm1">Got news?<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm12">Oake's Treehouse<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm7">Quest Questions and Answers<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm3">Stories<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm8">Item and Equipment Grab Bag<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm9">Dear Santa...<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm6">Agendas, Plans, and Procedures! - Guildites Only<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm4">A safe place to gripe! - Guildites Only<option value="thecoun